{
  "stem": "11589.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took about a week after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, as I said, you know, I used to write this diary about the people, you know, that I knew, and the sketches that I made, and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took it with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought, well, I'll have something to show for people, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it didn't work out, you know, because, as I said, the KGB stepped in inside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw with the other side on the train, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stepped in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They start asking people open up their luggage, you know, what they have, the few things they have.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're looking for some stuff that's against the Communist-- Communist Party, you know, against their laws, against their ideals.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew that if they found this diary with me, I'll be sent back to Siberia, because this is anti-Russian, to write the truth about them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, the people who were involved there, the names that I had, it's very bad for them too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, as I said before, they were at the other side of the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I opened up the window a little bit and threw it out, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That way, I came back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the first thing I stopped was the little town where I lived, you know, Zdolbunow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did you find when you got there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found something like you going in a desert, you know, and you find here and there, you know, a-- something that grows wild, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't know what it is and everything strange.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People, you know, you don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People are walking by, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You look at them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't even know them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The neighborhood where I lived, you know, I went through.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
